metadata.name: SAD
metadata.description:
In this (current) Sat0shi-era, there is a lot of effervescence, energy flows & as one can see, the outter part is representing that crazy battle of a million souls. 

In the middle of all that, appears the King of the seas, symbol of the ultimate goal: the Whale fucken level. 

Poor souls, the market maker they all seek to beat in their greedy quests, is the one feeding on them everytime.
